N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 15 ยง 125.4 - Transfer of cases

State Regulations

If a complaint made returnable before the bureau alleges an
offense other than a traffic infraction, the complaint will be transferred to a
tribunal of appropriate jurisdiction. Notes
